<h2 id="POtIiKbRQNuZuYwSwdCgAeuyZhpQbmsv">What Are Computers Good At?</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p><span class="line-through">Basic math</span></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Simple decision making</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Doing things over and over again very, very fast</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><span class="line-through">And storing data</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
